.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\">推post</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5. 互like留言，推上FB留言熱門 <span style=\"color: red;\">(新嘗試！)</span><br />\n <br />\n是日精選@7 Dec 2019  <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>盞記</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nest1964/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnest1964%2F&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqrufZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=90c91b72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nest1964/</a></span></strong><br />\nFB search: 盞記<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>※留言template</strong></span></span><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">留言重點</span></strong>係全力阻止廣告商簽訂下年合約</strong> <br />\n <blockquote>無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故暫時罷用。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/77258400_511694166354104_6350063255410442240_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_ohc=0e_f7zjxvxMAQnZawxJpVhbjwCn17kwzV7iBVhcyMz4_9du-ognUo4TpA&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=4feba3de183c0595326f74914444ce69&amp;oe=5E81433E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F77258400_511694166354104_6350063255410442240_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_ohc%3D0e_f7zjxvxMAQnZawxJpVhbjwCn17kwzV7iBVhcyMz4_9du-ognUo4TpA%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3D4feba3de183c0595326f74914444ce69%26oe%3D5E81433E&h=66cb63cf&s={SIZE